    <item>
      <title>How to mirror iPhone to iPad?</title>
      <link>https://damirche.com/blog/2025-01-12-how-to-mirror-iphone-to-ipad/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 09:10:48 -0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://damirche.com/blog/2025-01-12-how-to-mirror-iphone-to-ipad/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;In this quick guide, you&amp;rsquo;ll learn how to mirror iPhone to iPad using the &lt;a href=&#34;https://damirche.com/products/vlogmonitor&#34; &gt;VlogMonitor app&lt;/a&gt;.
Even as VlogMonitor is designed for vloggers who need lower latency, higher framerate, and quality, the app is perfectly good
for &amp;ldquo;just&amp;rdquo; screen mirroring, though it might be a bit of overkill. ðŸ˜Ž&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;VlogMonitor is stupidly simple and easy to use. Honestly, you do not need to read this post because the app will guide you
to the desired result. I designed it with simplicity in mind and worked really hard to optimize latency and quality.
But let&amp;rsquo;s get started.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;On iPhone&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;on-iphone&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#on-iphone&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;steps hx-ml-4 hx-mb-12 ltr:hx-border-l rtl:hx-border-r hx-border-gray-200 ltr:hx-pl-6 rtl:hx-pr-6 dark:hx-border-neutral-800 [counter-reset:step]&#34;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Open VlogMonitor&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;open-vlogmonitor&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#open-vlogmonitor&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://damirche.com/blog/2025-01-12-how-to-mirror-iphone-to-ipad/open.webp&#34;
    alt=&#34;Open VlogMonitor&#34; width=&#34;220&#34;&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Tap Record&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;tap-record&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#tap-record&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://damirche.com/blog/2025-01-12-how-to-mirror-iphone-to-ipad/record.webp&#34;
    alt=&#34;Tap Record&#34; width=&#34;220&#34;&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Tap Start Streaming&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;tap-start-streaming&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#tap-start-streaming&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://damirche.com/blog/2025-01-12-how-to-mirror-iphone-to-ipad/start-streaming.webp&#34;
    alt=&#34;Tap Start Streaming&#34; width=&#34;220&#34;&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Select Start Broadcast&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;select-start-broadcast&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#select-start-broadcast&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Allow Local Network Access if asked.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://damirche.com/blog/2025-01-12-how-to-mirror-iphone-to-ipad/start-broadcast.webp&#34;
    alt=&#34;Select Start Broadcast&#34; width=&#34;220&#34;&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Streaming will start in a few seconds.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;On iPad&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;on-ipad&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#on-ipad&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;steps hx-ml-4 hx-mb-12 ltr:hx-border-l rtl:hx-border-r hx-border-gray-200 ltr:hx-pl-6 rtl:hx-pr-6 dark:hx-border-neutral-800 [counter-reset:step]&#34;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Open VlogMonitor&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;open-vlogmonitor-1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#open-vlogmonitor-1&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://damirche.com/blog/2025-01-12-how-to-mirror-iphone-to-ipad/open-ipad.webp&#34;
    alt=&#34;Open VlogMonitor&#34; width=&#34;330&#34;&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Tap Watch&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;tap-watch&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#tap-watch&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://damirche.com/blog/2025-01-12-how-to-mirror-iphone-to-ipad/watch.webp&#34;
    alt=&#34;Tap Watch&#34; width=&#34;330&#34;&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Tap Search for Devices&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;tap-search-for-devices&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#tap-search-for-devices&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Allow Local Network Access if asked.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://damirche.com/blog/2025-01-12-how-to-mirror-iphone-to-ipad/search.webp&#34;
    alt=&#34;Tap Search for Devices&#34; width=&#34;330&#34;&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Select your iPhone&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;select-your-iphone&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#select-your-iphone&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://damirche.com/blog/2025-01-12-how-to-mirror-iphone-to-ipad/select-iphone.webp&#34;
    alt=&#34;Select your iPhone&#34; width=&#34;330&#34;&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That&amp;rsquo;s it! At this point, you&amp;rsquo;ll see your iPhone&amp;rsquo;s screen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

